high_descs: Walk over to the other side of the wooden table.
Pick up the head of lettuce off of the wooden table.
Walk over to the kitchen sink.
Put the head of lettuce in the kitchen sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean head of lettuce.
Turn around and walk over to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the clean head of lettuce inside on top of the plate, then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean head of lettuce on a plate in the fridge.

high_descs: Walk to the other side of the table on your left.
Grab the lettuce from the table.
Walk to the kitchen sink behind you.
Put the lettuce in the sink, wash it, then grab it.
Walk to the fridge behind you and to your right.
Put the lettuce in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Wash lettuce for storage in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn and go to the other side of the table where the lettuce is.
Pick up the lettuce that is on the table.
With the lettuce in hand turn and go to the sink.
Place the lettuce in the middle of the sink and turn the water on to wash it.  Turn the water off and pick it up.
With the lettuce in hand go to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the lettuce to the left of the tomato on the top shelf on top of the object that is there.
anns.task_desc: Wash and place lettuce in fridge.
